00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:50.000
A really great cast that the director uses

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:53.000
to tell the different stages of love: 

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:57.000
youth, played by Riccardo Scamarcio, Valeria Solarino and Laura Chiatti,

00:05:57.000 --> 00:06:01.000
maturity with Carlo Verdone and Donatella Finocchiaro and 

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:04.000
